        • queue_of_facts
          LinkedBlockingQueue<HashMap<ModelView,FactType>> queue_of_facts
          The queue of facts. The key is the model and the value is the type of fact that is associated with the model, so that the view can update the model accordingly. The queue is a FIFO queue, thread-safe and blocking. We need an HashMap because we need to eventually store null values as keys.
